org.barghos.core.api.tuple

Interface ITup3dR

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITup3R, ITupdR, ITupR
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PTup3d, Tup3d

    public interface ITup3dR
extends ITupdR, ITup3R
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 3-dimensional double tuple.
